OL,3,CPolice clash with protesters close to
OL,4,Cwhere Henry Nowak was stabbed to death
OL,6,FPolice holding riot shields have
OL,7,Fclashed with protesters close to where
OL,8,FHenry Nowak was stabbed to death.
OL,10,FA police helicopter hovered overhead
OL,11,Fas officers were pelted with stones on
OL,12,Fa residential street in the St Denys
OL,13,Farea of Southampton, before they
OL,14,Fcharged with perspex shields in an
OL,15,Fattempt to push the crowd back.
OL,17,FDemonstrators chanted "Henry, Henry"
OL,18,Fas the line of police were pelted with
OL,19,Fbricks and forced to retreat again.
