OL,3,CPolice clash with protesters close to
OL,4,Cwhere Henry Nowak was stabbed to death
OL,6,FFollowing the protest outside
OL,7,FSouthampton Central Police station, a
OL,8,Flarge group walked across town to the
OL,9,Farea of St Denys, close to where the
OL,10,Fmurder took place.
OL,12,FChairs, cans and flares were thrown at
OL,13,Fpolice in riot gear, eventually
OL,14,Fforcing officers and three police vans
OL,15,Fback from the line they had been
OL,16,Fholding.
OL,18,FThis is a breaking news story, more to
OL,19,Ffollow........
